  <summary date="2020-04-17T21:39:31Z" status="Introduced in House">Correct the Census Count Act

This bill requires the Department of Commerce, beginning with the 2030 decennial census, to attribute an individual incarcerated in a correctional center to such individual's last place of residence before incarceration.</summary>
